buildInventoryList

public java.util.Vector buildInventoryList(java.lang.String strSecurity,
                                           neuragenix.security.AuthToken authToken)
                                    throws neuragenix.dao.exception.DAOException,
                                           java.sql.SQLException,
                                           java.lang.Exception
This method queries the database and get the details required to list the inventory which is the name and ID's of the sites,Tanks,Boxes and Trays

Parameters:
strSecurity - the permission that needs to be checked before performing this action
authToken - The authorization token which holds all the permissions for this user/session
Returns:
returns a Vector of Site objects indicating the Sites that are available in this inventory
Throws:
neuragenix.dao.exception.DAOException - this is the Exception that is thrown by the DALQuery
java.sql.SQLException - this is the Exception that is thrown by the DALQuery
java.lang.Exception - this is the Exception that is thrown by the DALQuery
